==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Celtic
<hw>Celt"ic</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The language of the
Celts.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The remains of the old Celtic language are found in the
Gaelic, the Erse or Irish; the Manx, and the Welsh and its cognate
dialects Cornish and Bas Breton.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Celticism</ent>⟦br⟧
